snippet.title: C64 Game: Macbeth
snippet.description:
Completed the first part but got stuck on the second, even using an online solution.

Released in 1984 by Creative Sparks / Thorn Emi Computer Software and developed by Oxford Digital Enterprises (https://www.mobygames.com/company/oxford-digital-enterprises-ltd).

Review: https://archive.org/details/Big_K_Issue_09_1984_Dec/page/n15/mode/2up
